 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A post\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"@sunisalee\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"effortless\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The morning podium training workout here prior to Saturday's Winter Cup was Lee's first public workout since last year's national championship in August, which came five months after she was diagnosed with an incurable kidney disease.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.85128538948646, \"rank\": 0.1746941327765477, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The morning podium training workout\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday's Winter Cup\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's national championship\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"an incurable kidney disease\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The disease, which she has not identified by name, came on suddenly, swelling her joints and causing rapid weight gain that made it impossible to compete, shelved her elite competition and ended her plans to continue herNCAAcareer at Auburn.\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auburn_Tigers_football\", \"score\": 0.6903207358862427, \"rank\": 0.4485925374537551, \"text\": \"Auburn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auburn_Tigers_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auburn_Tigers_football\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The disease\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"name\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"her joints\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"rapid weight gain\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"her elite competition\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"her plans\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"herNCAAcareer\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement Lee went from dreaming of chasing another all-around medal to simply hoping she could compete again as doctors first worked to accurately diagnose her condition and then find the proper medication cocktail to keep it at bay.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 986, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.85128538948646, \"rank\": 0.1746941327765477, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another all-around medal\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"doctors\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"her condition\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"the proper medication cocktail\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"bay\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The toll on her body was enormous, but her psyche took an even bigger hit.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The toll\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"her psyche\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"an even bigger hit\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that took a little setback when I got sick,\\\" Lee said Friday.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.85128538948646, \"rank\": 0.1746941327765477, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little setback\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got nervous.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't sure I was good enough to make theOlympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said she wasn't in the \\\"greatest mindset.\\\"\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\\"greatest mindset\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her coach, Jess Graba, is much more direct.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her coach\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"Jess Graba\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's been very depressed all year,\\\" he said, using the word three times to describe the athlete he's coached since she was 6.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the word\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two have weathered plenty of storms before, Lee's career beset by injuries and her Olympic journey delayed by the global pandemic, but nothing compares to this.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\":