ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At first I did not even want her to do gymnastics.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just wanted her to come and hang out, do stuff.\\\"\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Progress, once measured in literal leaps and bounds, instead came in baby steps.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Progress\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"literal leaps\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"bounds\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"baby steps\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Lee felt stronger, she frequented the gym more, using her body to gauge how hard she could work.\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.85128538948646, \"rank\": 0.1746941327765477, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fumbling around a little bit in the dark,\\\" is how Graba describes the early days of navigating Lee's health challenges with her gymnastics training.\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2433, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.85128538948646, \"rank\": 0.1746941327765477, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C